readme:
Service Usage

This services provides the ability to search and match parties using Biographic data with filters of context.
The search is conducted using a client's Birth Year as well as either a Generic Identifier or a client's Documents Details.
If a single client is matched confidentally, Biographic and associated IDs will be returned in the Response with a Confidence Percentage.
